    "content" : "Hi All\n<br> \n<br> So the resto of my bus got finished last year, I managed to do like 30 miles, but they were the best 30 miles ever !\n<br> \n<br> The bus then went into storage for the winter in Cornwall, I actually live in Austria up in the Alps and I'm back in the UK next week which got me thinking......\n<br> \n<br> Rather than fly back to Austria from the UK .... why don't I just get the bus out of storage and drive it home !\n<br> \n<br> Is this bad / mad idea based on how \"new\" it all is .... or should I just man up and get on with it ?\n<br> \n<br> Cheers\n<br> \n<br> Nik",
